      "title": "Sri Lankan arrested by Maldives police",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A Sri Lankan citizen who participated in a protest against the Maldivian government for providing safe haven to President Gotabaya Rajapaksa, who escaped from Sri Lanka early on Wednesday (13), was arrested by the country's police."
